nodes.text: Brainworm Rot Type C was a subtype of the Brainrot Plague that originated on Neimoidia, a planet notorious for its frequent quarantines. It was this attribute that led Ebenn Q3 Baobab, after serving as a Neimoidian fleet doctor, to joke that "the principal export of the Neimoidian home planet is Brainworm Rot Type C".
